Onsite

1. OO design. A game, with NxN grid. One person plays white and the other plays black;
They take turns to place dot on the grid. Every time, they choose a column and the dot will fall till it hits a occupied dot or the boundary of the grid.
If a person's color achieves 4 dots along a diagonal or a row, then the person wins.
Note: it is important to determine the winning condition
